Before invoking [`getPageSource()`](https://stackoverflow.com/a/49081962/7429447) ideally you need to induce [WebDriverWait](https://stackoverflow.com/a/48990165/7429447) for the [_visibilityOfElementLocated()_](https://stackoverflow.com/a/49749804/7429447) for any of the static and _**visible**_ element on the page.


----------


An example
----------
As an example to extract the _page_source_ of _Google Home Page_ you need to wait for the _Search Box_ to be _**visible**_ as follows:

	ChromeOptions options = new ChromeOptions();
	options.addArguments(&quot;--headless&quot;);
